=== Seat Sync Flow ===
1. Member joins via accept_pending_invites_v1
2. Row inserted into public.tenant_memberships
3. on_membership_insert_sync_seats trigger fires
4. trigger_seat_sync reads service_role_key from vault
5. net.http_post calls sync-seat-count Edge Function
6. Edge Function counts all active tenant_memberships for tenant
7. Edge Function finds seat item via STRIPE_PRICE_ID match
8. Edge Function updates Stripe subscription quantity (absolute recomputation)
9. Sync failure is non-blocking -- membership always created

Same flow on DELETE for member removal.

=== Idempotency ===
Seat count uses absolute recomputation from DB state.
Duplicate trigger calls set same quantity -- cannot overbill.

